<document>

  <properties>
    <title>Create mapper index step</title>
    <author email="jourdren@biologie.ens.fr">Laurent Jourdren</author>
  </properties>



  <body>

    <section name="Create mapper index step">

      <p>This step allow to create index for all the mappers available in Eoulsan. This step is <b>automatically called when needed</b>
         and <b>must not be added to the workflow file</b>.</p>

      <ul>
        <li><b>Internal name</b>: genericindexgenerator</li>
        <li><b>Available</b>: Both local and distributed mode</li>

        <br/>
        <li><b>Input ports</b>:
           <ul>
             <li><b>genome</b>: genome sequence file (format: genome_fasta)</li>
             <li><b>genomedescription</b>: genome description (automatically generated from genome sequence file)</li>
           </ul>
         </li>

         <br/>
         <li><b>Output port</b>:
           <ul>
             <li><b>output</b>: genome mapper index</li>
           </ul>
         </li>

         <br/>
        <li><b>Optional parameters</b>: none</li>
      </ul>
    </section>


  </body>

</document>
